8PUZZLE:******************************************************************
**************************************************************************

8PUZZLE uses ncurses:
this will need to be installed in your linux terminal. To do so type: 
sudo apt-get install libncurses5-dev libncursesw5-dev

after you have this installed, simply run the program by using the Makefile's make command
and then ./myprogram
please keep the terminal window as large as possible when you run to prevent formatting issues
 






